{"tid":2263002,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果 khabib vs adesanya，邊個會贏","createTime":"2020-10-29T14:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T05:36:03.000Z","uid":343680,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba8cc44083d81f69e6a0e13888f30387cc20c821","tid":2263002,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"假設大家磅數一樣，<br />\n你地覺得邊個會贏？<br />\n兩個都好屈<br />\n一個屈身高同打法<br />\n另一個屈摔技<br />\n而兩個都係好體力＋耐打<br />\n<br />\n我個人鐘意 adesanya 多D<br />\n但係覺得 khabib會贏既機率係 6:4<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> khabib<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />adesanya"},{"pid":"0ea5a8965a7de13f14747fe1329eb793e82a3de2","tid":2263002,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T17:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866583c5f3d48af68a19d70e257ffe5ad2d114d8","tid":2263002,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T19:58:16.000Z","msg":"火影打站立勁臂展長<br />\n雖然瘦但抗打能力其實好好<br />\n但防摔唔算勁<br />\n<br />\n小鷹抗打能力都勁<br />\n唔需要同你打站立<br />\n最可怕就係打地面<br />\n 應該小鷹贏"},{"pid":"792e1fe6d61195a03739d659d77625c6e8184bab","tid":2263002,"uid":226560,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T20:08:05.000Z","msg":"一定中二贏 磅數都差成30磅 <br />\n站立一定khabib輸<br />\n就算khabib帶到落地打都未必食得住中二"},{"pid":"83ee434d4ece6f16cd3fb0d20ba98649b312ab7c","tid":2263002,"uid":226560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T20:09:37.000Z","msg":"唔同磅數無乜好比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6e8eb79364b1ca19edf70fbb0bdbf488ad027c","tid":2263002,"uid":158071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"輕d好似khabib著數d"},{"pid":"0b2bbf7cf508cd000463fe5038b52e4f068d5355","tid":2263002,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"792e1fe6d61195a03739d659d77625c6e8184bab","tid":2263002,"uid":226560,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T20:08:05.000Z","msg":"一定中二贏 磅數都差成30磅 <br />\n站立一定khabib輸<br />\n就算khabib帶到落地打都未必食得住中二"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"假設大家磅數一樣"},{"pid":"3d28dd4b22437a5423d92543550a33a82a3f89b6","tid":2263002,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"巴打你到底咩事要去新嗰個ufc post搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個post爆咗喺度答你<br />\n搏擊嘅本質就係要殺死對方，但宜家運動化之後嘅規則就可以保護運動員<br />\n你話cool頸會死，咁其實就咁出拳都可以打死人，咁按你邏輯係咪連出拳都要禁埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩個時候就突顯拳證（唔係裁判，裁判負責計分）嘅重要，所以拳證係一個專業嚟，佢要以保護拳手為前提去中止比賽。你有時會見到有人一拳比人knock down咗起唔返身佢就會飛身撲埋去中止比賽，又或者地戰時比人鎖頸，拳手真係會投唔切降就暈咗，拳證又會check實發現佢失去意識又會分開雙方。可能你冇試過窒息啦，其實暈同死中間都有一段長距離嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔使咁擔心冇咁易死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能係我認真咗，但我希望你或者其他睇到嘅人個對搏擊運動有更多認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外想補充一下yan犯規，準確嚟講係「三點著地，腳唔可以攻擊頭」。頭先個case係膝同兩隻腳掌形成三點，其他情況例如 手+雙腳都係三點著地，咁就唔可以用腳攻擊頭"}]}